summary: Just a player home that ive started working on in my free time, havent done much other than the exterior. Id like some feed back and suggestions on what to do with it thus far. A few things i know i need to finish are the hatchery and the garden. I dont have much experience with scripting and the like but i think this is a neat looking house.
